                                                              <br/> 
                                <div class="phototagleft">
                                  
                                </div>
                                                          </div>
                                                                                            <p><strong>Olga Zilberbourg</strong> has three books of fiction published in Russian and has published English-language fiction, essays, and book reviews in various publications. Her first collection in English, <em>Like Water and Other Stories</em>, is forthcoming in 2019. Raised in St. Petersburg, she now makes her home in San Francisco.</p>

                                            <div class="clear"></div>
                                                          
